-de.toem.impulse.samples.ISamples-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.getReference()=<b>public de.toem.impulse.samples.ISamples getReference()</b><br/>Returns the referenced samples object.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#getReference-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-boolean-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.goPrev()=<b>public boolean goPrev()</b><br/>Go to previous sample.<br/> <pre><br/> Example (JavaScript)<br/> <br/>  console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/>  if (in0.goPrev())<br/>     console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/> </pre><br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#goPrev-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-boolean-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.goNext()=<b>public boolean goNext()</b><br/>Got to next sample.<br/> <pre><br/> Example (JavaScript)<br/> <br/>  console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/>  if (in0.goNext())<br/>     console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/> </pre><br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#goNext-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-boolean-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.hasPrev()=<b>public boolean hasPrev()</b><br/>Returns true if a previous sample is exists.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#hasPrev-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-boolean-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.hasNext()=<b>public boolean hasNext()</b><br/>Returns true if a next sample is exists.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#hasNext-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-boolean-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.goPos1()=<b>public boolean goPos1()</b><br/>Goto first sample. Returns true if index was changed.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#goPos1-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-boolean-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.goEnd()=<b>public boolean goEnd()</b><br/>Goto last sample. Returns true if index was changed.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#goEnd-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-void-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.setIndex(int)=<b>public void setIndex(int index)</b><br/>Sets the samples index (0<count-1).<br/> <pre><br/> Example (JavaScript)<br/> <br/>  console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/>  in0.setIndex(in0.getCount()-1);<br/>  console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/> </pre><br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#setIndex-int-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-int-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.getIndex()=<b>public int getIndex()</b><br/>Returns the current index.<br/> <br/> <pre><br/> Example (JavaScript)<br/> <br/>  console.println(in0.getIndex());<br/>  in0.goNext();<br/>  console.println(in0.getIndex());<br/> </pre><br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#getIndex-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-int-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.getMaxIndex()=<b>public int getMaxIndex()</b><br/>Returns the maximal index.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#getMaxIndex-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-int-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.getMinIndex()=<b>public int getMinIndex()</b><br/>Returns the minimal index.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#getMinIndex-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-long-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.getUnits()=<b>public long getUnits()</b><br/>Returns the position of the pointer (to be multiplied with the domain base). The position may not be identical with the<br/> position of the indexed event (getUnits() != unitsAt(getIndex()).<br/> Same as getUnits(false)<br/> <pre><br/> Example (JavaScript)<br/> <br/>  console.println(in0.getUnits());<br/>  in0.goNext();<br/>  console.println(in0.getUnits());<br/> </pre><br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#getUnits-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-long-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.getUnits(boolean)=<b>public long getUnits(boolean atSample)</b><br/>Returns the position of the pointer (to be multiplied with the domain base). if atSample==true, the position is identical with the<br/> position of the indexed event (getUnits() == unitsAt(getIndex()).<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#getUnits-boolean-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul><li><b>atSample</b> If true, the method returns the position of the indexed event. <br/> <pre><br/> Example (JavaScript)<br/> <br/>  console.println(in0.getUnits());<br/>  in0.goNext();<br/>  console.println(in0.getUnits());<br/> </pre></li></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-de.toem.impulse.domain.DomainValue-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.getPosition()=<b>public de.toem.impulse.domain.DomainValue getPosition()</b><br/>Returns the position of the pointer. The position may not be identical with the position of the indexed event (getPosition()<br/> != positionAt(getIndex()).<br/> Same as getPosition(false)<br/> <br/> <pre><br/> Example (JavaScript)<br/> <br/>  console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/>  in0.goNext();<br/>  console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/> </pre><br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#getPosition-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-de.toem.impulse.domain.DomainValue-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.getPosition(boolean)=<b>public de.toem.impulse.domain.DomainValue getPosition(boolean atSample)</b><br/>Returns the position of the pointer. if atSample==true, the position is identical with the<br/> position of the indexed event (getPosition() == positionAt(getIndex()).<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#getPosition-boolean-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul><li><b>atSample</b> If true, the method returns the position of the indexed event. <br/> <pre><br/> Example (JavaScript)<br/> <br/>  console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/>  in0.goNext();<br/>  console.println(in0.getPosition());<br/> </pre></li></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-void-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.setDelta(long)=<b>public void setDelta(long delta)</b><br/>Internal use only! Sets the delta between position and the position of the indexed event (getUnits() - unitsAt(getIndex())<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#setDelta-long-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul><li><b>delta</b> Domain distance as a multiple of its domain base (e.g. domain base=1ms; units = 100; -> domain value = 100ms).</li></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-long-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.getDelta()=<b>public long getDelta()</b><br/>Returns the delta between position and the position of the indexed event (getUnits() - unitsAt(getIndex())<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#getDelta-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-void-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.setUnits(long)=<b>public void setUnits(long units)</b><br/>Sets the position of the pointer.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#setUnits-long-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul><li><b>units</b> Domain position as a multiple of its domain base (e.g. domain base=1ms; units = 100; -> domain value = 100ms).</li></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-void-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.setPosition(de.toem.impulse.domain.DomainValue)=<b>public void setPosition(DomainValue position)</b><br/>Sets the position of the pointer.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#setPosition-de.toem.impulse.domain.DomainValue-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul><li><b>position</b> Domain position as a DomainValue object (combination of domain base and factor).</li></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
