-void-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.setChanged(boolean)=<b>public void setChanged(boolean changed)</b><br/>Clear the changed flag (usually handled by an attached iterator).<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#setChanged-boolean-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul><li><b>changed</b> TODO</li></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.relative(java.lang.String)=<b>public de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer relative(String delta)</b><br/>Returns a new pointer with relative position.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#relative-java.lang.String-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul><li><b>delta</b> Domain distance as a text describing the domain value (e.g. 10ms).</li></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
