-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.relative(long)=<b>public de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer relative(long delta)</b><br/>Returns a new pointer with relative position.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#relative-long-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul><li><b>delta</b> Domain distance as a multiple of its domain base (e.g. domain base=1ms; units = 100; -> domain value = 100ms).</li></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
