-java.lang.String-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.format(int)=<b>public java.lang.String format(int format)</b><br/>Formats the current group/sample using format 'format'.<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#format-int-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul><li><b>format</b> Format specifier as defined in ISample.FORMAT_.. (e.g. ISample.FORMAT_HEXADECIMAL)</li></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
-int-de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer.defaultFormat()=<b>public int defaultFormat()</b><br/>Returns the default format ( ISample.FORMAT_...).<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/IPointer.html#defaultFormat-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.IPointer</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>format specifier as defined in ISample.FORMAT_.. (e.g. ISample.FORMAT_HEXADECIMAL)
